Contributing to Project Tick
============================

Firstly, Please read GOVERNANCE

Quick Start
-----------

Please read the docs/handbook/ for the section you are interested in. Example: MNV

Commit Messages
---------------

===TXT
project(component): short description

Explanation of what and why.
===

Examples:

MeshMC(fix): fix crash on startup with invalid config

DCO Sign-off
------------

Every commit must include a sign-off line and all files to commit:

===SH
git commit -s -a
===

This adds:

===TXT
Signed-off-by: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
===

The bot enforces DCO compliance and labels PRs missing sign-off.

Documentation
-------------

See `docs/` for detailed documentation:

- docs/handbook/ - Handbook

Contact
-------

- Issues: GitHub Issues[1]
- Bugs: Project Tick Bugzilla[2]
- Email: projecttick@projecttick.org

License
-------

By contributing, you agree to license your work under the project's licenses.
See LICENSES/ folder.

